The '''Squib [[Trade language/Legends|Trade Language''']] was a parallel language spoken by the [[Squib/Legends|Squib]] species. Although not as widespread as the [[Squibbian]] language itself, most Squibs were also fluent in the Squib Trade Language.

Squibs only used the Squib Trade Language to trade among themselves, which allowed them to do without alerting other beings of their goals. Non-Squibs were never taught this language.

